name: 【Style】 Illustrator Style BUNBUN | abec | LoRA
description:
[Style] Illustrator Style BUNBUN | abec | LoRA

This LoRA is an attempt to get the style of the magnificent illustrator BUNBUN(aka abec). He is well known as an illustrator of light novels in the Sword Art Online universe. BUNBUN Illustrations.

«Imitation is the most sincere form of flattery.» ― once said Oscar Wilde.

Trained on Anything-v4.5.

Should work without trigger words, but just in case add bunbun

Recommended parameters:

  • LoRA weight: 0.5-0.9

  • Sampling method: Euler a or DPM++ 2M Karras or SDE

  • Sampling steps: 28

  • CFG Scale: 4-8

  • Upscaler: Latent

  • Denoising strength: 0.5

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned or other

P.S. The most beloved illustrator.
